{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "9d86d49b-4b69-479b-bc2b-bfd1d4bb5a78",
    "name": "Binance Futures Market Data - REST and WebSocket",
    "description": "Public Binance futures market-data collection for USD-M and COIN-M futures.\n\nDefaults use BTC contracts. Change collection variables such as usdm_symbol, usdm_stream_symbol, coinm_symbol, and coinm_stream_symbol for other markets.\n\nREST requests are public market-data endpoints and do not require API keys. WebSocket entries use wss:// URLs; in Postman, open them as WebSocket requests and click Connect. For live subscription examples, connect to the Dynamic Subscribe requests and send the JSON payload shown in the request description.\n\nDocs:\n- USD-M REST: https://developers.binance.com/docs/derivatives/usds-margined-futures/market-data/rest-api\n- USD-M WebSocket: https://developers.binance.com/docs/derivatives/usds-margined-futures/websocket-market-streams\n- COIN-M REST: https://developers.binance.com/docs/derivatives/coin-margined-futures/market-data/rest-api\n- COIN-M WebSocket: https://developers.binance.com/docs/derivatives/coin-margined-futures/websocket-market-streams",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
